line_1: As Tully with philosophy once dealt,
line_2: Who deal with scripture, its importance felt,

line_1: And as Her Son has to My Bosom dealt
line_2: That constant Flame, which faithful Henry felt:

line_1: But He, who Silence loves; and never dealt
line_2: In the false Commerce of a Truth Unfelt.

line_1: To know they were in mercy dealt,
line_2: Thro' all the sorrows I have felt,
